        {
            "id": 6077482,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 康卡斯特(CMCSA-US)大跌5.03%，報33.59美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>康卡斯特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CMCSA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CMCSA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CMCSA-US</a>)截至台北時間25日22:11股價下跌1.78美元，報33.59美元，跌幅5.03%，成交量7,156,062（股），盤中最高價34.44美元、最低價33.59美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.07%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.16%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.19%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.28%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>康卡斯特(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:CMCSA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/CMCSA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">CMCSA-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.93%</li> <li>近 1 月：+0.45%</li> <li>近 3 月：+6.57%</li> <li>近 6 月：-5.98%</li> <li>今年以來：-5.76%</li></ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6077482",
